snippet.title: Kathleen Daily
snippet.description: Daily, Kathleen Anne "Kathie" (Nee O'Brien) Born Good Friday, April 3, 1942, in Peoria, IL. Longtime resident of Elm Grove, WI. Was surrounded by her loving family as she went home to God on Wednesday, March 16, 2011, after a courageous battle with cancer. She will be loved
